{"id":"b1a4b90f90a8b8d1cb29838ec0ea98a4d97a7a97","url":"https://www.ithome.com/0/979/274.htm","title":"169 元绿联 Max5s 头戴式耳机开售：号称 AI 功能终身免费，续航 112 小时","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"IT之家 (ITHome)","byline":"作者：问舟","excerpt":"绿联 Max5s 头戴式蓝牙耳机正式开售，主打双金标认证音质、-45dB 深度降噪及 112 小时超长续航。其内置的 AI 助手功能承诺终身免费，支持录音转写、同声传译等实用场景，为百元级耳机带来新体验。#数码好物推荐# #蓝牙耳机#","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"paragraph\">\r\n            <p>感谢IT之家网友 <a href=\"https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2029428\" rel=\"nofollow\">华南吴彦祖</a> 的线索投递！</p>\r\n            <p data-vmark=\"0000\"><a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/\" target=\"_blank\">IT之家</a> 7 月 21 日消息，绿联 Max5s 头戴式蓝牙耳机现已开售，定价为 169 元。该耳机获得国家 A 级降噪认证，号称 AI 功能终身免费，拥有双金标音质，深度降噪可达 -45dB，续航 112 小时。</p><dir><a contenteditable=\"false\" href=\"https://u.jd.com/9gGCYff\" target=\"_blank\" data-wapurl=\"https://u.jd.com/9O8Nkwo\" data-iosurl=\"https://u.jd.com/918HBMO\" data-androidurl=\"https://u.jd.com/9a84IRX\" data-hosnexturl=\"https://u.jd.com/9a8jWZT\" data-hosurl=\"https://u.jd.com/9r85QzZ\" data-uwpurl=\"https://u.jd.com/918eu2Y\" data-wxmpurl=\"ithome://openmp?appid=wx91d27dbf599dff74&path=%2fpages%2funion%2fproxy%2fproxy%3fspreadUrl%3dhttps%253a%252f%252fu.jd.com%252f9D8XZ3M%26EA_PTAG%3d17078.27.380\" data-itwxurl=\"https://u.jd.com/9rGLr3O\" data-lpwxurl=\"https://u.jd.com/9DGKirz\" data-ncid=\"199748\"><span><span><img src=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/472445/36/10664/48462/6a4ca40dF46b9786e/008332032096cc39.png\" w=\"800\" h=\"800\" title=\"169 元绿联 Max5s 头戴式耳机开售：号称 AI 功能终身免费，续航 112 小时\" data-original=\"https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/472445/36/10664/48462/6a4ca40dF46b9786e/008332032096cc39.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\"></span><span><span><span>京东</span><span>绿联 Max5s 头戴式蓝牙耳机</span></span><span></span><span><span> 169 元</span><span>直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p data-vmark=\"38c1\">2026 年数码家电政府补贴持续进行中，IT 之家为大家汇总国补领券地址，买数码家电之前记得领取。</p><p 